---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Joanne Charron | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Joanne Charron, Insurance Advisor at Heidi Blondin Financial. Over 27 years of experience in financial services, specializing in insurance solutions for individuals and families."
>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 items-start">

        <div class="md:col-span-1">
          <img
            src="/team/joanne-portrait.jpg"
            alt="Joanne Charron — Insurance Advisor, Heidi Blondin Financial"
            class="w-full aspect-square object-cover object-top"
          />
          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="font-serif text-xl text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Joanne Charron</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-ink/60 mt-1">Insurance Advisor</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-5">
            <p>With over 27 years of experience in the financial services industry, I am passionate about helping individuals and families achieve financial success through tailored insurance and financial solutions.</p>
            <p>Over the years, I have developed extensive expertise in mortgages, insurance solutions and credit products. My tenure at Clarica/Sun Life involved managing a book of business with over 4,000 clients and training multiple administrative assistants. I also served as Director of Sales and Service for two brokerages over the past 15 years, further deepening my leadership and operational experience.</p>
            <p>As a licensed Life Insurance Advisor, I have cultivated strong relationships with many of Canada's leading insurance providers. I specialize in solutions for hard-to-insure individuals, as well as group benefits, critical illness protection, health and disability coverage, and mortgage insurance.</p>
            <p>Beyond my professional work, I am deeply committed to community service. I proudly serve on the Executive Committee of the Army Navy Airforce Unit 377 in Kingston as Secretary and Public Relations Officer, supporting local fundraising and volunteer initiatives.</p>
            <p>In my personal time, I enjoy a variety of creative and outdoor pursuits that keep me energized and inspired. I love sewing and crafting, and I'm often out hiking, camping, or fishing from my kayak. I also stay active by playing in local baseball and billiards leagues—and when the weather's right, I hit the road on my motorcycle for a bit of adventure and fresh air.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="/heidi/" class="font-sans text-sm font-medium text-brand-gold underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-amber-700">← Back to the team</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <img src="/team/joanne-fishing.jpg" alt="Joanne fishing from her kayak" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
        <img src="/team/joanne-motorcycle.jpg" alt="Joanne on her motorcycle" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
        <img src="/team/joanne-woodworking.jpg" alt="Joanne woodworking" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
